---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 198
  - Title: Yesod Hayirah
    Location: 66
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Humility=Obscurity
  - 56
---
Wouldst thou raise up thy head to carry the crown and diadem of pride
with a name of praise, understand, that the God who alone is clothed
in the garment of excellency, unto whom alone greatness belongeth.
bringeth low unto dust the high, and raiseth on high those who are
low.
